					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11601702#post-4256895</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11601702/scp-4143#post-4256895</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2019 22:35:33 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Khaim</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1796098</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Exploration dates are inconsistent. The description says initial exploration was in May 2038, but the addendum says January.</p> <p>Also, minor nitpick but I really dislike the DD-MM-YYYY format. It's exactly backwards from the proper YYYY-MM-DD (which has identical lexicographic and chronologic order).</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
