					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11601702#post-4247080</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11601702/scp-4143#post-4247080</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2019 06:31:52 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Lt Flops</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1735419</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Apart from a literal holy shit, this has <em>me</em> going &quot;holy shit&quot;. This is incredibly bizarre. This is like ten exploration logs in a single person's intestine. And honestly, I was already hooked and in upvote territory by the containment procedures alone, which is really saying something. There is often little narrative weight in containment procedures, but not here; this has a ton of personality. More people should strive for this level of narrative complexity in containment procedures, really &#8212;</p> <blockquote> <p>Anomalies released from defecation are to be contained or neutralized through all necessary means.</p> </blockquote> <div style="text-align: right;"> <p>And talk about a wham line!</p> </div> <hr /> <p>I really like this. +1 for a wacky extradimensional portal to (or from?) Satan's anus.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
